Maybe it's also an issue in the Azure SearchStore implementation and metadata keys should never go into the primary level of a schema.

Compare:

```json
{
  "id": 1234,
  "vector": [0.123, 0.567, ...],
  "_text": "Abcdefgh"
}
```

vs

```json
{
  "id": 1234,
  "vector": [0.123, 0.567, ...],
  "metadata": {"_text": "Abcdefgh"}
}
```
